# âš–ï¸ let vs const vs var (Important)

Difference:

let:

* changeable
* block scope
* modern

const:

* not changeable
* block scope
* modern

var:

* changeable
* function scope
* old

# ğŸ§  Block Scope Example

{
  let a = 10;
  const b = 20;
  var c = 30;
}

console.log(c); // 30
console.log(a); // error
console.log(b); // error
```

Because:

let & const â†’ block scope
var â†’ function/global scope

